@startuml
'https://plantuml.com/sequence-diagram

autonumber

title Register an Aircraft Model: Simplified Sequence Diagram

actor "Backoffice Operator" as BO
participant ":System" as S

BO -> S: Types requested data \n(String name, double seating_capacity,\ndouble max_range, double fuel_capacity\ndouble cruising_speed, String manufacturer_name)
S --> BO: Confirms the (in)sucess of the operation

@enduml